<title>IN THE GARDEN OF EDEN</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien in Eden huonah,
 Nu leh Pa chuh hun siem in;
 Amau chuh kichen sakin,
 Vangphatna chuh A pie tai.

[V2]
 Lalpa vangphatna hun pie'n,
 Vawn zatam paibang kuoh di'n;
 Na lungtuok muolsuoh dingin,
 Changbang dam kumkhuo sawt hen.

[V3]
 2. Pientil thu gui bang zawtin,
 A chun-leh-zuo thuong nusie'n;
 Amau hi a kigawm tau,
 Kikhen kit ni neilo di'n.

[V4]
 3. Kilungsiet tuoh gel dingin,
 Ki-enkawl a dingguol di'n;
 Pumkhat a um muolsuok di'n,
 Lungkhat a tuibang luong di'n.

[V5]
 4. Pathien na chuh sem gel un,
 Chung thangvan na kaih tiengun;
 Sungkhat a khuoi bang lut di'n,
 Vana nawpna la sa di'n.</lyrics>
</song>